OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidely dry
OL,6,Fand very warm this evening, although
OL,7,Fisolated showers or thunderstorms
OL,8,Fcould affect the west of the region,
OL,9,Fthese largely easing overnight. Low
OL,10,Fcloud likely to spread inland from the
OL,11,Fcoast later accompanied by a
OL,12,Fstrengthening breeze.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FLow cloud soon clearing to
OL,15,Fleave a mainly dry, bright day with
OL,16,Fjust a chance of evening showers.
OL,17,FFeeling much fresher in the brisk
OL,18,Feasterly breeze, but still warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
