OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FVariable cloud, very warm or hot on
OL,7,FThursday and Friday with clear or
OL,8,Fsunny periods, but also a risk of
OL,9,Fshowers or thunderstorms. Very warm,
OL,10,Fpotentially hot on Saturday still.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
